"title": "9612: hope, in God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9612: hope, in god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A total grounding of one's confidence and expectation in God's goodness and providential care even in the face of trouble.</p>\n<h2>Hope in God is commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps131:3\">PSA 131:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:24\">PSA 31:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:7\">PSA 130:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a></p>\n<h2>Hope can be placed in Scripture as the word of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:74\">PSA 119:74</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:43\">PSA 119:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:49\">PSA 119:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:81\">PSA 119:81</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:114\">PSA 119:114</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:147\">PSA 119:147</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:5\">PSA 130:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:4\">ISA 42:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:6\">ACT 26:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Hope can be placed in God in the face of difficulty or trial</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:5\">PSA 42:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:2\">EZR 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:16\">JOB 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:15\">JOB 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:18\">PSA 9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:19-Ps25:21\">PSA 25:19–25:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:116\">PSA 119:116</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:19\">JER 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:5\">1TI 5:5</a></p>\n<h2>The outcome of hoping in God</h2>\n<h3>It brings security and confidence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:5\">PSA 146:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:18\">JOB 11:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:3\">PSA 25:3</a> <em>There is no shame for those who hope in the LORD</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:17-Ps33:18\">PSA 33:17–33:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:20-Ps33:22\">PSA 33:20–33:22</a> <em>The LORD helps and protects those who hope in him</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:7\">PSA 39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:9\">PSA 52:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5\">PSA 71:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:11\">PSA 147:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:22\">JER 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:21-Lam3:22\">LAM 3:21–3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:15\">ACT 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:12\">ROM 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:10\">1TI 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to specific results</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:9\">PSA 37:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:31\">ISA 40:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:22\">PSA 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:5\">PSA 62:5</a> <em>rest</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:14\">PSA 71:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:14-Prov24:16\">PRO 24:14–24:16</a> <em>wisdom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:5\">ISA 51:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11\">JER 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:25\">LAM 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:12\">ZEC 9:12</a> <em>restoration</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:18\">ROM 4:18</a> <em>the example of Abraham's hope</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">ROM 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:7\">2CO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15\">2CO 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:25\">2TI 2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a> <em>eternal life</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:5\">1PE 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>",
